<dd>As I have said elsewhere, I have a great deal of respect for many of the admins who supported this council.  I just find the action wrongheaded, and can&#39;t see that it could possibly be of any practical use at this point in time, where so many people oppose its very existence in the current format.  And I do not oppose the goals, I oppose the implementation.  <a href="" title="User:Who then was a gentleman?">Who then was a gentleman?</a> (<a href="" title="User talk:Who then was a gentleman?">talk</a>) 22:06, 12 July 2009 (UTC)
